race.comment: THINK TANK (1) is building to a win and put the writing on the wall last time when runner-up at the provincials latest, narrowly beaten. Peaks now and gets chance. EASY BEAST (2) was solid two back then raced on speed but outclassed last time in tougher. Well placed this company and should be a big improver. AMBER NOOK (3) has been mixing form but is suited here and has the ability. Wide draw but trip suits. GREATESTOFEASE (7) was well backed at Manangatang last weekend and charged home to score a big win. Fit and in form and can go close again. HIT THE SLOPES (5) is suited by the extra trip and can do much  better.
